{
  "stem": "10272.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were marching-- we didn't know exactly where we were marching to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We already on the seventh day of the march.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were so exhausted, that if this-- if we wouldn't much into this town, into a town-- and our guards told us we are here, keep it up, another few-- another mile or two, we are-- we are dead.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this give us more energy to keep up this march, and to straighten out, and to show for the village, for the people of the city that we are not-- we are-- we are man.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We can walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We can take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we had this yellow band on our hand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all-- they all stopped to-- to-- to watch us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who are these guys coming in?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had this on our-- we had the feet bags and we had everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had the blankets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were dressed up properly against the cold, with shoes, and boots, with-- with gloves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were-- we kept going now already, and we reached a place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, to halt, to stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We looked around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw there a building of three floor-- about three, four floor building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there's a sign that says, the Headquarters of the Nilosh-- Nilosh party or something or-- I don't know what it was, something about the Nilosh headquarters, in Kormend.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the city, we understood, it was called Kormend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it's supposed to be a city which here, they will-- they will take us from here to Germany, or hand us over to the Germans, something like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we are waiting in line there, three, three, three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the first three guys were supposed to get inside, get registered, and pass a medical check up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's what the officer told us, walking in with all-- everything he has on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we are waiting for these three guys to come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It took about 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And these-- when-- when three-- these three characters came out, we didn't recognize them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were so badly beaten.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were dressed in-- in such a dirty and-- and-- and torn [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] pants.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he had a jacket without-- without a shirt, shoes without laces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the other guy couldn't even put on the shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The shoes were smaller with-- with one size.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He couldn't put them on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to come barefoot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was bleeding from the nose from-- the eyes were swollen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he hardly could walk and talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As they came to us, and we were going to see what happened, they dropped on the floor-- on the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now the officer didn't know what to do, our crew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To send more through?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just couldn't believe it what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but all of a sudden, one-- we had a guy who was our-- not-- he was not in charge, but he was our leader.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We recognized him as a leader.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his name was-- was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Pishto, ?] big guy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We called him the big guy, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Poli. ?] [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Poli. ?] That was the big guy in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, we are going in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he first told us we drop everything on the street, what we have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All-- all the valuables we had to throw away on the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only thing which-- which I left for myself was the-- the postcard which I kept-- [SOBBING] I kept in my hand, my fist.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not throw away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I kept my shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I kept my underwear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And maybe I kept a sweater too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when-- when-- but my turn didn't come yet, because before there was-- there were other boys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the guy who was religious, the religious guy I mentioned, he put on quickly this [NON-ENGLISH] this kind of a-- how do you call it-- the [NON-ENGLISH], when they pray in the morning.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he put on-- on his head, the tallit and he start-- start praying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we all throw on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kids come around and they grabbed everything from the street and they run away with all the belongings which we had and bring it to them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we moved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our turn came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the other guys didn't come out already to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they kept them in the backyard, so the people on the seat wouldn't see in what shape-- so we shouldn't see in what shape they are coming out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So three, three, three, went in, went in, till my turn came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I went in with-- with Benjamin-- Benjamin and [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Loti, ?] my friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we walked in-- the [INAUDIBLE] was-- the walkway inside the building.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
